all but the core classes, especially Wizards, Paladins and Necromancers need something so that a group takes them instead of a second Warrior.</P><P>Nerfing is never a good choice, but mighty classes set high standarts...</P><P>Fey<BR>45 Druid<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
