o the same to the enchanters and any other class that would be needed like that.</P><P>I think to make a class more wanted by giving them more abilitys to be able to do another classes job to a degree makes things more difficult than they already are. When change a  classes role then it effects other classes and ectra. </P><P>I think for them to make one class more group friendly by adopting anothers role would result in rebalancing half the classes in the game. It would be much easyer and alot less work to find another way of doing it.<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
